gamerule.deathTime.description: How many times players need to have to be reincarnated.
gamerule.fullOfSeed.description: Set if players will always get Demon Lord Seed or Light Spirit.
gamerule.imRimuru.description: Set if players will be 'Rimuru' when reincarnated.
gamerule.instantReincarnate.description: Set if players will instantly reincarnated after joining the world.
gamerule.lorewiseOtherworlder.descriptio: Set if only lorewise Otherworlders will spawn.
gamerule.magiculeLimit.description: Set the limit amount of magicule one player can have.
gamerule.magiculePlundering.description: Set if players can plunder each other's Magicule instead of Max with certain skills.
gamerule.noNether: No access to the Nether after reincarnated.
gamerule.noNether.description: Set if players will no longer can access the Nether after reincarnated.
gamerule.opRace.description: Disable to forbid the use of random-only races such as Demon.
gamerule.playerPlunder.description: Disable to prevent players to plunder skills from each other.
gamerule.racePlus.description: Enable to allow the players to choose the Demon race without the need of random.
gamerule.randomPlunder.description: Disable to remove plundering/copying skills from the Skill Random Chance when reincarnating.
gamerule.randomRace.description: Set if players won't be able to choose race after reincarnating.
gamerule.skillGriefing.description: Whether some skills should be able to change/break blocks, this might lead to some skills being useless.
gamerule.soulAmount.description: Amount of Soul to become a True Demon Lord
gamerule.spatialSpectator.description: Set if players can use Spatial Skills to acces Spectator Mode, this might lead to some skills being useless.
gamerule.spawnDistance.description: Set the max distance from 0 the player will get teleported.
